Create Aggregate / Tiers:

Aggregate: Collection of 1 more raid groups.
            Collection of disks defines raid on top of disks
            
            1. Root Aggregate: Contains OS, Firmware files, logs
            2. Data Aggregate: contains volumes for data provisioning

RAID Types:
          RAID 4 - 1 dedicated parity disk
          RAID DP - 2 dedicated parity disk - dedicated dual parity
          RAID TEC - 3 dedicated parity disk - Triple Eraser Coding


